//Paraspinal mass

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Paraspinal mass' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and selected by default
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected by default
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
